    "rank": 5,
    "text": "You launch a curved length of wood at a foe that arcs around objects and obstacles to strike from an unexpected direction. Make a spell attack roll against the target\u2019s AC. This attack ignores the target\u2019s concealed condition and ignores all cover except greater cover. If you hit, the projectile deals 7d10 bludgeoning damage.",
